Package: cassidyr
Title: Connect to CassidyAI API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jacob", "Dennen", , "jdenn0514@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive R interface to the CassidyAI API,
    enabling seamless integration of AI-powered assistants into R workflows.
    Create conversation threads, send messages, and build interactive chat
    applications with context-aware AI assistance. Designed for survey
    researchers, data analysts, and R developers who want to leverage
    large language models in their work.
